# Hydroseed Inc. Premium Redesign Demo (Astro)

This repository contains a complete outreach/demo redesign for **Hydroseed Inc.**, focused on hydroseeding, lawn installation, erosion control, and post-installation support across Greater Michiana.

## Stack used
- **Astro** for fast static pages and strong SEO output.
- **Custom CSS design system** in `src/styles/global.css` for premium, easy-to-edit styling.
- **Lightweight native animation layer** (IntersectionObserver + CSS transitions) for scroll reveals/parallax without heavy dependencies.

## Second-pass visual + interaction polish (this update)
- Rebuilt the visual system with deeper color tokens, larger type scale, richer shadows, and improved spacing rhythm.
- Redesigned the hero with a layered project-preview composition, service-type selector chips, stronger trust framing, and CTA microcopy.
- Added reveal-on-scroll and staggered card animations plus subtle parallax on major hero visuals.
- Added a “Find the Right Starting Point” service-fit selector section.
- Added a stylized map-style service area section.
- Added a quote expectations section (“What happens after you request a quote?”).
- Upgraded before/after area with a premium comparison-style placeholder module.
- Improved contact and detail-page presentation so the site feels less generic and more sales-ready.

## Project goals implemented
- Premium local-service design with contractor-grade credibility.
- Conversion-focused quote path with repeat CTAs, click-to-call, sticky mobile quote CTA, and scroll-triggered desktop quote bar.
- Unique service/location pages and local-intent internal linking.
- Structured SEO metadata and JSON-LD schema helpers.
- Intentional image placeholder system ready for replacement with approved project photos.

